國際衝突期間，強姦可能會變得系統化，[[战争时期的性暴力|战争时期的性暴力]]及[[性奴隸|性奴隸]]便是其中兩例。該些行為屬[[危害人类罪|危害人类罪]]及[[战争罪|战争罪]]。當強姦與意圖全部或局部消滅目標種族的行為一同進行時，其便成了[[种族灭绝|种族灭绝]]罪行的一項元素。

受害者可能會因此產生[[心理創傷|心理創傷]]及患上[[創傷後壓力症候群|創傷後壓力症候群]]<ref name="aaets">{{cite web |url=http://www.aaets.org/article178.htm |title=Post Traumatic Stress Disorder in Rape Survivors |publisher=The American Academy of Experts in Traumatic Stress |year=1995 |accessdate=2013-04-30 |archive-date=2019-09-13 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190913203354/http://www.aaets.org/article178.htm |dead-url=no }}</ref>。強姦可對當事人的身體產生嚴重傷害，並使其面對[[意外懷孕|意外懷孕]]及患上[[性傳播疾病|性傳播疾病]]的風險。受害者還有可能被施行者以至其家屬或家庭成員暴力對待及威脅<ref name="zeenews.india">{{cite web |url=http://zeenews.india.com/news/uttar-pradesh/rape-victim-threatened-to-withdraw-case-in-up_694364.html |title=Rape victim threatened to withdraw case in UP |publisher=Zeenews.india.com |date=2011-03-19 |accessdate=2013-02-03 |archive-date=2019-02-27 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190227181949/https://zeenews.india.com/news/uttar-pradesh/rape-victim-threatened-to-withdraw-case-in-up_694364.html |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref name="wisemuslimwomen">{{cite web |url=http://www.wisemuslimwomen.org/currentissues/stigmitizationofrape/ |title=Stigmatization of Rape & Honor Killings |publisher=WISE Muslim Women |date=2002-01-31 |accessdate=2013-02-03 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20121108041415/http://www.wisemuslimwomen.org/currentissues/stigmitizationofrape/ |archive-date=2012-11-08|deadurl=yes }}</ref><ref name="bbc">{{Cite newspaper |last=Harter |first=Pascale |url=https://www.bbc.co.uk/news/world-africa-13760895 |title=BBC News - Libya rape victims 'face honour killings' |journal=BBC News |date=2011-06-14 |accessdate=2013-02-03 |archive-date=2013-09-21 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130921101600/http://www.bbc.co.uk/news/world-africa-13760895 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。
